  "texts": [
    "We extend the analysis from Figure 5 to all heads by aggregating attention into five categories: URL prefix, domain, suffix, boc, and eoc.",
    "We then normalize these values to obtain a probability distribution and compute the entropy.",
    "Low entropy values indicate a concentrated distribution-approaching a one-hot vector-which signals a significant attention sink on the URL prefix.",
    "These patterns are illustrated in Figure 13.",
    "We also show the training loss curves for models prepending different portions of the URL in Figure 12."
